{
  "page": "Green Grace",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Green Grace</b> is the high priestess of her order, the <a href=\"/index.php/Graces\" title=\"Graces\">Graces</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari\" title=\"Ghiscari\">Ghiscari</a> religion. There appears to be only one Green Grace in each Ghiscari city.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The Green Grace at the <a href=\"/index.php/Temple_of_the_Graces\" title=\"Temple of the Graces\">Temple of the Graces</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> is <a href=\"/index.php/Galazza_Galare\" title=\"Galazza Galare\">Galazza Galare</a>, for instance, and there is an <a href=\"/index.php/Green_Grace_(Astapor)\" title=\"Green Grace (Astapor)\">unnamed Green Grace</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Temple_of_the_Graces_(Astapor)\" title=\"Temple of the Graces (Astapor)\">corresponding temple</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a>. \"Your Benevolence\" is a style used to refer to Green Graces.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Known_Green_Graces\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known Green Graces</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Grace&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Grace&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/23/The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png/300px-The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"385\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/23/The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png/450px-The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/23/The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png/600px-The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Green_Grace_by_Naomimakesart.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Galazza_Galare\" title=\"Galazza Galare\">Galazza Galare</a>, the Green Grace of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>, by Naomimakesart ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The Green Grace of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Galazza_Galare\" title=\"Galazza Galare\">Galazza Galare</a>, acts as an advisor to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_of_Meereen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Queen of Meereen\">Queen of Meereen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Two of Daenerys's favorite <a href=\"/index.php/Cupbearers_of_Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Cupbearers of Daenerys Targaryen\">cupbearers and hostages</a> are <a href=\"/index.php/Qezza\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Qezza\">Qezza</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Grazhar\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Grazhar\">Grazhar</a>, cousins to the Green Grace.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Green_Grace_(Astapor)\" title=\"Green Grace (Astapor)\">Green Grace of Astapor</a> remains unnamed. During the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Astapor\" title=\"Siege of Astapor\">siege of Astapor</a>, their Green Grace has a vision that <a href=\"/index.php/Cleon\" title=\"Cleon\">Cleon</a>, the Butcher King, can save the city from the besieging forces of <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a>, despite the fact that the man was already dead and buried. The corpse of Cleon is fitted back into his <a href=\"/index.php/Armor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Armor\">armor</a> and strapped onto the back of a starving <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">horse</a>, which leads the remnants of his new <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a> on a failed sortie. They encounter a legion from <a href=\"/index.php/New_Ghis\" title=\"New Ghis\">New Ghis</a>, however, and are all killed. For her failed prophecy, the Green Grace of Astapor is impaled upon a stake in the <a href=\"/index.php/Plaza_of_Punishment\" title=\"Plaza of Punishment\">Plaza of Punishment</a> and left there until she dies.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Quentyn_Martell\" title=\"Quentyn Martell\">Quentyn Martell</a>, one of the besiegers, recalls the priestess in her torn robes, impaled upon a stake and attended by a cloud of glistening green flies.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Green_Graces\">Known Green Graces</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Grace&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Green Graces\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Galazza_Galare\" title=\"Galazza Galare\">Galazza Galare</a>, the Green Grace of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Green_Grace_(Astapor)\" title=\"Green Grace (Astapor)\">Unnamed Green Grace</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Green_Grace&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Appendix\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_70\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 70\">Chapter 70</a>, The Queen's Hand.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_2\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 2\">Chapter 2</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_23\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 23\">Chapter 23</a>, Daenerys IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_30\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 30\">Chapter 30</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_25\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 25\">Chapter 25</a>, The Windblown.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404132520\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.038 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.040 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 487/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8746/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2044/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 141/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2841/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   22.434      1 -total\n 78.41%   17.591      6 Template:Ref\n 48.78%   10.942      6 Template:Ref/core\n 18.57%    4.167      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:10592-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404132520 and revision id 334617\n -->\n",
